Requirements

Plain Network Publishing would like to publish a church directory. This software solution will manage the household entries and automatically create a print-ready publication.

  


To make it easier to enter existing information, each household can automatically create child households.

  


Initially, all households will share the same numbers as the existing directory. However, these will eventually be renumbered to a new numbering scheme.
